Exact Solitary-wave Solutions for the General
Fifth-order Shallow Water-wave Models

We perform a computerized symbolic computation to find
some general solitonic solutions forthe general fifth-order shal-
low water-wave models. Applying the tanh-typed method, we
have found certain new exact solitary wave solutions. The pre-
viously published solutions turn out to be special cases with
restricted model parameters.
